# ─── SECRETS — NEVER COMMIT ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# User config contains API keys (Groq, Grok, Gemini) and Slack tokens.
# Config lives at ~/.config/linux-speech-flow/config.json — never in the repo.
config.json
*.secret
*.key
*.token
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ─── PROJECT PLANNING (GSD / Claude Code internal — not part of the release) ──
.planning/
.claude/

# ─── USER DATA — never commit ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SQLite history lives at ~/.local/share/linux-speech-flow/history.db
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# contains the LiteLLM API key
litellm.md
